                              <abbr>ሚካ፡</abbr> (<ref target="#ms_i1.1"/>) for
                              <expan>ሚካኤል፡</expan></item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ሰላ፡</abbr> (<ref target="#ms_i1.1"/>) for <expan>ሰላም፡</expan>
                           </item>
                        </list>
                     </handNote>
